Ascurpic - Asc' Your Picture
============================

License: GPL v3
Author:  ubitux [www.pilule-rouge.net]

Requirements:
------------

 - *nix

Compilation:
-----------

% make re

Usage:
-----

Usage: ./ascurpic -f <filename> -t <filename> -o <filename> [-s <num> -n <num> -c <num>]

 -f <filename>  Bitmap to convert. This parameter needs the -t and -o ones.
 -t <filename>  File with some text to use
 -o <filename>  The Web Page you want to generate
 -s <num>       Font size (in px)
 -n <num>       Number of char for 1px
 -c <color>     Background color in hex (e.g. : -c a0b1c2)

Examples:
--------

% ./ascurpic -f examples/tux.bmp -t examples/tux.txt -o examples/tux.htm
% ./ascurpic -f examples/kodamas.bmp -t examples/kodamas.txt -o examples/kodamas.htm -c 000000
